    "created_at": "2024-06-01T11:35:47Z",
    "updated_at": "2024-06-01T11:35:47Z",
    "body": "Yes, you are right. This is indeed an upstream error. However, before waiting for upstream repairs, I would like to attach my current solution here. This could potentially help others : \r\n- Comment \"mkdir ~/.cache/starship\" and \"starship init nu | save -f ~/.cache/starship/init.nu\" in  `nu.env-path`\r\n- Change the path in starship init nu to a double slash ",
